These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
City: hamburg, boston, colone
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, crime, epic
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, fuchsia
 1. the person who likes grey is the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person watching epic movies and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 5. the designer is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person traveling to colone is the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person who likes grey is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| City         | boston    | colone  | hamburg        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Movie-Genre   | crime     | satire  | epic       |
| Color         | grey     | lavender | fuchsia |

