.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, jet-ski
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking, hiking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia, marigold
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the british##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person driving the van is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Transport          | van    | quad-bike | jet-ski          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Hobby           | reading        | hiking      | filmmaking         |
| Flower         | begonia | sunflower  | marigold |

