.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, kale, peas
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, dancer, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, march, november
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia, tulip
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person who growstulip is the dancer##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the social-worker is between the person who growszinnia and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the person who growszinnia is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | peas      | kale      | cabbage      |
| Job         | software-developer   | social-worker | dancer |
| Birthday   | january | march    | november          |
