The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, april
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person playing billiard and the person traveling to new-york##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | billiard | domino      | scrabble      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| City   | hamburg  | paris     | new-york |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Birthday     | may        | april        | june   |

