.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra, davidoff
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, gamesy, pink
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, aconite
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who likes chestnut and the manager##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the musician and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
9. the person who likes gamesy is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar      | game      | alhambra      | davidoff       |
| Food          | mango      | pumpkin    | broccoli   |
| Hobby         | singing    | baking     | hiking     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| Color   | gamesy    | pink    | chestnut       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Flower     | begonia       | daisy | aconite |

