.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, july, january
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, havana, bongani
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
House: victorian, modern, ranch-style
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person driving the roller is the victorian house##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fisherman is the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the havana-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Birthday          | june   | january   | july  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Cigar   | alhambra   | havana     | bongani  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| House         | modern | victorian   | ranch-style  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 